{"tid":1236704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請大家停止分化論！！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-17T13:13:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T13:51:57.000Z","uid":167468,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"405bdf4203e20ec8074e99324aea664403db17b1","tid":1236704,"uid":167468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:13:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再互相話大家係分化撚啦</span><br />\n無論係和理非抑或勇武派，互相指責大家係對事情冇幫助㗎。<br />\n衝嘅唔係鬼，再話係分化，到時就冇人幫和理非衝<br />\n和理非係幫手聚集民意，冇咗民意，勇武就要單打獨鬥<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兩邊<span style=\"color: red;\">缺一不可</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">槍口對外</span>啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n請大家理性討論，大家有分辨是非既能力，<br />\n倘若真係分化嘅就唔好回覆，<br />\n兩邊已經有好多人心灰意冷。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">我地仲有好長嘅路要行落去㗎，唔好放棄大家！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"68d7fc5fd4ff574bdf13f476bbdbf551d30e04e7","tid":1236704,"uid":119667,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:14:20.000Z","msg":"雙方應互相配合<br />\n而非各有各做"},{"pid":"4464c16ad6430b8bf5f470f3f670ee6d22dad655","tid":1236704,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:14:50.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-------------------<br />\n[求推]勇武派及快樂抗爭派請進(好重要)<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1235241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1235241</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上「和理非&gt;deadline &gt;衝，重複直至成功」正正就係馬丁路德金同Malcolm X嘅做法<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1235655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1235655</a>"},{"pid":"a31d14b321eb548d608efdf042925cb0a1a01fa3","tid":1236704,"uid":2896,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:15:47.000Z","msg":"唔該幫手一齊周圍post：<br />\n反送中Deadline、黑警、醫管局、所有被捕政治犯、撤回暴動定性。<br />\n不分化、不割蓆、不篤灰、不譴責。加油！"},{"pid":"dbac0d03da204a1